## Architecture Plan

### New Components

**`src/components/ManualTimeEntryModal.tsx`**
- Modal for creating time entries without timer
- Fields: Description, Project, Start date/time, End date/time (or duration)
- Duration calculator: Can enter either end time OR duration
- Validation: End time must be after start time
- Save to IndexedDB via store

**`src/components/ProjectManager.tsx`**
- Project CRUD interface (create, edit, delete projects)
- Project list with color coding
- Used in Settings page or TimeTracking page
- Fields: Name, Color, Description, Active status

**`src/components/ProjectSelector.tsx`**
- Dropdown component for selecting project
- Used in timer panel and manual entry modal
- Shows project color dot + name
- "No Project" option

**`src/components/MonthlyTimeReport.tsx`**
- 30-day calendar grid with daily totals
- Hover to see entries for that day
- Monthly total card
- Average per day calculation
- Project breakdown (if projects enabled)

**`src/components/TimeEntryCalendar.tsx`**
- Full calendar view (similar to Calendar widget)
- Time entries shown as blocks on calendar
- Click to view/edit entry
- Visual representation of work distribution

**`src/components/BulkActionsBar.tsx`**
- Appears when entries selected in TimeEntryList
- Actions: Delete, Change project, Export selected
- Select all / Clear selection buttons

